title: Bikerumor Pic Of The Day: Bridger-Teton National Forest, Wyoming
content:
Photo submitted by Ben Donnelly, “Green River Lakes Bridger-Teton National Forest, Wyoming. After 50 miles of slogging through loose chunk and fighting dusty headwinds, the views (and the swim in the lake) were worth it.” We always love seeing photos from where you are riding and are happy to share them with our readers around the world […]
